^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Let's specifically discuss the auction 1D-P-2C. In SAYC it only promises 10 points. But if you have less than an opening hand, you cannot have a 4-card major. In that case you cannot afford to take a 2nd bid over 2C if partner makes a minimum rebid.|
